    "description": "<p>Founded in 2008 by Serge Trigano and his sons Jérémie and Benjamin, Mama Shelter is a creator of living spaces and a daily director!<br>\n<br>\nWe create atypical places where everyone feels at home, places born of a blend of influences, freedoms, sensations and emotions. Each Mama tells the story of the city in which it is located, and all influences blend together. More than rooms and restaurants, Mama Shelter hotels have an energy, a vibrancy; they are true urban refuges. Mama Shelter is a place to live life to the fullest: it's irreverent, popular, sassy, and sexy.<br>\n<br>\nMama Shelter spans three continents, nine countries and fourteen cities, with more openings in the pipeline. Mama Shelter is part of the Ennismore collective, a creative hotel group rooted in cultures and destinations. Ennismore is a JV with Accor, the largest hospitality company in Europe.</p>",
